underlying_goal: Diagnose and create a robust plan to fix a Flash of Unstyled Content (FOUC) issue.
primary_success: Created a comprehensive, multi-layered plan to fix a FOUC issue, and then successfully orchestrated a review of that plan with other AI agents to incorporate their feedback and make it even more robust.
brief_summary: To fix a 'flash of unstyled content', Claude first performed a root-cause analysis and created a detailed plan involving a pre-init script. At the user's request, it then had the plan reviewed by other AI agents, synthesized their feedback, and produced an even more robust final plan for implementation.
